            <title><![CDATA[찬성 여론 업은 기시다 “7월 총선 개헌 공약”]]></title>
            <link>https://www.khan.co.kr/world/japan/article/202205032214035/?utm_campaign=list_click&amp;utm_source=reporter_article&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=%EB%B0%95%EC%9D%80%ED%95%98_%EA%B8%B0%EC%9E%90%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80</link>
